actions.title: Deployment proxy
actions.description: This a required contract to initialize all other contracts. It is simple wrapper around EIP-2470 Singleton Factory that emits an event of contract deployment. The wrapper also validates if the deployment was successful.

actions.title: Governance initiation data
actions.description: This contract will contain the expected addresses of some of the contracts that will be deployed

actions.title: Cora Timelock Controller
actions.description: A Timelock needed for the governor to add a delay for execution to the approved DAO proposals

actions.title: Cross-Chain Message Relayer
actions.description: Cross-Chain Message Relayer to execute cross-chain DAO proposals

actions.title: Cora Governance
actions.description: Cora protocol governance contract. It will apply and manage DAO proposals.

actions.title: Treasury Boostrapping
actions.description: Treasury Boostrapping contract to bootstrap the treasury with the initial CORA tokens
